snippet.title: Aero Attack Trailer
snippet.description:
quasiStudio is a brand-new mobile game development and design agency, and we're proudly presenting our very first game - Aero Attack - which we have finally finished after months of work. 

Help Bob survive this retro fun-filled space arcade, with minions, cows, and a couple of more surprises waiting for you around the corner!

Check out our website at http://quasi.studio/

and make sure to follow us at

Instagram - http://www.instagram.com/quasi.studio
Twitter - https://twitter.com/quasistudio/
